ActCanada Marine Act
SubjectRemoval of municipal director of the Oshawa Port Authority - Bruce McArthur
PrecisOrder approving the REMOVAL of BRUCE McARTHUR as the director of the Oshawa Port Authority, who was appointed by the City of Oshawa, to ensure that membership of the Hamilton-Oshawa Port Authority's Board of Directors is consistent with the provisions of the Canada Marine Act, effective June 16, 2019.
